OL,3,CDriver sentenced after crashing into
OL,4,Ctwo parked cars in police chase
OL,6,FA drunk driver has been sentenced
OL,7,Fafter running through five red lights
OL,8,Fand crashing into two parked cars.
OL,10,FDeclan Muers was arrested after he was
OL,11,Fcaught speeding through Nottingham
OL,12,Fcity centre in the early hours of 18
OL,13,FFebruary.
OL,15,FMuers was spotted by officers driving
OL,16,Fdangerously along Maid Marian Way.
OL,18,FThey then chased him before the
OL,19,Fpursuit ended on Hungerhill Road, St
OL,20,FAnn's after he lost control of his
OL,21,FVolkswagen Scirocco.
