OL,3,CDriver sentenced after crashing into
OL,4,Ctwo parked cars in police chase
OL,6,FOn Monday 7 October, the 27-year-old
OL,7,Fpleaded guilty to dangerous driving,
OL,8,Ffailing to stop for police and driving
OL,9,Fwhilst drunk.
OL,11,FHe was later was jailed for 16 months,
OL,12,Fas well as being suspended for two
OL,13,Fyears at Nottingham Crown Court.
OL,15,FAfter being breathalysed, Muers was
OL,16,Ffound to be 14mg of alcohol over the
OL,17,Flegal limit, which is 35mcg of alcohol
OL,18,Fper 1000 millilitres of breath.
