OL,3,CDriver sentenced after crashing into
OL,4,Ctwo parked cars in police chase
OL,6,FThe court heard there were a lot of
OL,7,Fpeople out at the time enjoying the
OL,8,Fweekend.
OL,10,FNo pedestrians were injured in the
OL,11,Fchase.
OL,13,FMuers sustained a minor head injury
OL,14,Fafter crashing into two parked cars
OL,15,Fand was taken to Queen's Medical
OL,16,FCentre for treatment.
