OL,3,CDriver sentenced after crashing into
OL,4,Ctwo parked cars in police chase
OL,6,FThe driver was also further
OL,7,Fdisqualified from driving for two
OL,8,Fyears, given a four-month curfew and
OL,9,Fordered to complete ten rehabilitation
OL,10,Factivity requirement days.
OL,12,F"He should have got a taxi home but
OL,13,Fseemingly didn't want to pay a fare"
OL,15,FFollowing the sentencing, PC Fraser
OL,16,FHeaton, of Nottinghamshire Police,
OL,17,Fsaid:
