OL,3,CDriver sentenced after crashing into
OL,4,Ctwo parked cars in police chase
OL,6,F"Muers showed a clear disregard for
OL,7,Fthe safety of others by driving
OL,8,Fdangerously through a city centre in
OL,9,Fpoor weather conditions.
OL,11,F"He was in no fit state to be behind
OL,12,Fthe wheel of a car and it is fortunate
OL,13,Fhe didn't cause harm to another road
OL,14,Fuser or pedestrian. He was also
OL,15,Fextremely lucky not to have sustained
OL,16,Fa more serious injury himself after
OL,17,Flosing control and crashing into two
OL,18,Fparked vehicles.
