OL,3,CDriver sentenced after crashing into
OL,4,Ctwo parked cars in police chase
OL,6,F"During his police interview, he told
OL,7,Fus he'd been drinking in a nightclub
OL,8,Fand left after becoming angry about
OL,9,Fsomething that had happened.
OL,11,F"He should have got a taxi home but
OL,12,Fseemingly didn't want to pay a fare.
OL,13,FNow he's paid a heftier price in court
OL,14,Fwith the loss of his driver's licence."
